Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:252273,253316}Why?{NOTE:じゃあ何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:18.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:254025,258988}Even though they tried, Lilia and the Felyne Network couldn't tell us where Avinia is.{NOTE:リリアたちやアイルーネットワークでもアユリアの居場所は分からないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:24.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:258988,264118}Plus, the Ebon Riders will be coming to places where they can harbor more Kinship Stones.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズが絆石狩りをしそうな場所にこっちから出向くんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.28,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:264118,266287}And you think they'll come in this direction?{NOTE:それがあっちだと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:31.79,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:266287,271793}Chief Omna says there are some hidden Rider villages in that direction.{NOTE:オムナ村長の話だとあっちにはいくつかライダーの隠れ村があるからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.96,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:271793,273961}Hmm. Fine, then.{NOTE:ふむ。まあいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:38.67,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:273961,278674}But if we don't find anything there,\Nwe'll just return here and go Navirou's way.{NOTE:あっちに何もなければここに戻ってナビルーが選んだ道を行けばいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:278674,282470}If we keep walking, we'll eventually find our goal.{NOTE:くじけず歩み続ければおのずと道は開ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:47.18,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:282470,287183}Sometimes good things happen when Navirou says good things…{NOTE:このナビルーがいいこと言ってるときにはいいことが起こったりするからな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:287183,290311}…Hey! Wait for me!{NOTE:…って待て待て待て～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:57.15,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:294106,297151}Lute and Navirou never change.{NOTE:相変わらずだね、リュートとナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.07,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:297151,300071}Which way would you like to go, Cheval?{NOTE:シュヴァルさんはどの道を進みますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.24,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:300655,303241}I want to find out more about the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:俺はブラックライダーズのことをもっと調べたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.03,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:304283,308037}So it's probably better to go to a port town where we can collect more information.{NOTE:だから情報が集まる港町に行くのがいいと思ってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.08,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:308037,309080}My thoughts exactly.{NOTE:同感です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:16.42,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:309747,316420}By the way, Mille, Hyoro and Nariki should be here, here and here.{NOTE:ちなみにミルさんヒョロさんナリキさんたちは今ごろこことこことこの辺りにいるはずです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.08,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:316420,317088}Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.96,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:318047,321968}We discussed the search routes with the Numbers before leaving.{NOTE:出発前にナンバーズのみんなと捜索ルートを話し合ったよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.92,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:321968,322927}Good.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:26.68,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:322927,326681}Each one chose a place where it's easiest for them to gather information.{NOTE:それぞれ情報を集めやすい土地を選び向かっています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.01,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:326681,329016}Everyone in the Numbers went with their Navigator.{NOTE:ナンバーズのみんながナビに付いてくれて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.39,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:329016,330393}It's reassuring.{NOTE:…心強いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:330393,333479}But Navirou's navigation is still as bad as ever.{NOTE:ナビルーのナビは相変わらずのようですが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:39.73,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:335565,339735}But I still believe in the strength of Lute and Navirou's kinship.{NOTE:でも俺リュートとナビルーの絆の強さを信じてるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.99,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:341612,344991}I feel like they'll be able to do something we can't.{NOTE:俺が予想もできないようなことをしてくれる気がする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.15,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:344991,346158}I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.45,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:346158,349453}In other words, you have faith in them.{NOTE:つまり信頼しているということですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.53,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:349453,350538}Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.21,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:354750,358212}"Do something we can't", huh?{NOTE:予想もできないようなこと…か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:358212,359505}Interesting.{NOTE:面白え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.54,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:359505,361549}Let's make sure it's true.{NOTE:なら見せてもらうとするか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:07.34,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:362717,367346}Master Gale doesn't like to stay idle.{NOTE:仕掛けられるより仕掛ける方が好きだからなゲイルさまは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.56,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:376063,377565}There's nothing here…{NOTE:何もない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:377565,379358}No donuts either…{NOTE:ドーナツもない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.11,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:379358,382111}No clues on where is Avinia…{NOTE:アユリアの手掛かりどころか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:382111,384864}No one… is here.{NOTE:誰も…いない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:29.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:384864,389118}You know, you're the one who ate all the donuts without thinking earlier.{NOTE:ドーナツは後先考えずに食いまくったお前のせいだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.32,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:389118,391329}Come on. Stand up.{NOTE:ほら。さっさと立って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.49,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:393831,395499}It's all Lute's fault…{NOTE:リュートのせいだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:395499,398377}It's because Lute chose this way!{NOTE:リュートがこっちの道を選んだせいだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.54,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:398377,399545}I'm done for…{NOTE:もう駄目だ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.29,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:399545,401297}I'm too tired to walk.{NOTE:疲れ過ぎて歩けない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:48.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:402673,408012}Then what was all that "if we keeping walking, we'll find our goal" you said before?{NOTE:ついさっきくじけず歩み続ければおのずと何とかって言ってたろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:408012,409680}I'm out of donuts!{NOTE:ドーナツ切れだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.76,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:409680,413768}Navirou's constitution makes it impossible to walk without donuts!{NOTE:ナビルーはドーナツが切れると歩けなくなる体質なんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.64,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:413768,416646}That's the first time I've heard that.{NOTE:初めて知ったぞその設定。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:416646,419357}Oh well, I guess I can just fly from here.{NOTE:まっ、でもそういうことなら飛ぶか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.02,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:419357,420024}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.19,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:420024,421192}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:423653,424654}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.03,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:428157,430034}I completely forgot about that!{NOTE:その手があったか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:430034,432620}Keep walking, Navirou!{NOTE:ナビルーは頑張って歩け～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:13.70,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:432620,433704}Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:28.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:448094,448928}Yo!{NOTE:よっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.22,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:448928,451222}I was just looking for you.{NOTE:ちょうどお前らを捜してたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.89,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:452932,453891}Me too.{NOTE:俺もだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.52,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:454934,457520}Did you want your butt handed to you by Master Gale so much?{NOTE:そんなにゲイルさまにやられたいのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.27,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:458562,460272}Where's Avinia?{NOTE:アユリアはどこだ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.31,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:460272,463317}I can't just tell you so easily.{NOTE:そいつは簡単には教えられねえなぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.15,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:464443,468155}Then what do we have to do for you to tell us?{NOTE:ん、ならどうすれば教えてくれるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.90,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:469281,470908}How about 100 donuts?!{NOTE:ドーナツ100個か!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.66,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:472410,475663}If you want information, you'll need to hand over your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:教えてほしけりゃ絆石をよこすんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:475663,479625}I have to admit, I'm interested in your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:まあ、確かに、お前の絆石には興味がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.33,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:479625,481335}Avinia's too, right?{NOTE:アユリアのもだろ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.67,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:481335,483671}And that's why you kidnapped her!{NOTE:だからアユリアを連れていったんだろ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.67,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:483671,484672}Why are you doing this?{NOTE:何でだよ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.17,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:484672,488175}And what's that secret art from Avinia's village?{NOTE:何なんだよ!?アユリアの村に伝わる秘術って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.17,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:489260,491178}I'd like to know that too.{NOTE:俺も知りたいねぇ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:492263,494181}You don't know it either?{NOTE:お前も知らないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.93,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:495057,497935}Only Master Anvis knows that.{NOTE:それをご存じなのはアンヴィスさまだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.10,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:498769,500104}Anvis…?{NOTE:アンヴィス？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.98,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:500104,501981}Is he your boss?{NOTE:そいつがお前らのボスか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.85,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:501981,502857}Oops.{NOTE:ヤベ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:504150,506193}Master Anvis has nothing to do with it.{NOTE:アンヴィスさまは関係ねえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:506193,509196}I'm just doing what I have to.{NOTE:俺は俺のためにやるべきことをやるまでだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:509947,512658}And what exactly are you trying to do?{NOTE:お前何をしようとしてるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.24,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:513492,516245}Do you honestly think he'd tell you?{NOTE:正直に話すとでも思ってるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.24,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:516245,519248}Nuts! I don't remember telling you either.{NOTE:ナッツ！お前にも話した覚えはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.58,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:520207,523586}They don't seem to get along very well.{NOTE:あいつらあんまり仲良くないみたいだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.50,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:523586,526505}What are you planning to do with Avinia?!{NOTE:アユリアをどうするつもりなんだよ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.00,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:526505,528007}Beats me.{NOTE:さあな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:528007,529258}What the heck?{NOTE:何なんだよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.71,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:529258,530718}But you're a Rider just like us.{NOTE:同じライダーなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:533262,534680}We're nothing alike.{NOTE:同じじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:534680,536682}Me and you, at least.{NOTE:少なくとも俺とお前は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:536680,538267}That's not true!{NOTE:そんなことない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:538267,539810}We have a lot of things in common!{NOTE:ちょっと似てるところもある！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:05.64,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:541312,545649}"Things in common"?\NYou and Master Gale? What things?{NOTE:どこら辺が似てるっていうんだ？お前なんかとゲイルさまが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.06,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:545649,547068}Well…{NOTE:例えば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.15,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:547068,548152}I know!{NOTE:そう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:548152,550905}You also named your Monstie!{NOTE:お前もオトモンに名前を付けてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:550905,553115}Dusk… if I remember right.{NOTE:ダスク…だったよな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.41,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:554200,556410}Is that your reason…!?{NOTE:そんな理由かよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:556410,559121}But it's a proof that he thinks of his Monstie as a family!{NOTE:でもオトモンを家族だって思ってる証拠だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.37,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:560414,563375}He's a fellow Rider that cherishes the strength of his kinship, just like we do.{NOTE:絆の力を大事にしてるライダー同士だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:565419,566629}Kinship, huh?{NOTE:絆か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:567588,570132}We're totally different.{NOTE:だがやっぱりまるで違うな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.42,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:570132,571425}You and me.{NOTE:俺とお前は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.38,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:571425,572384}But why?!{NOTE:何でだよ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.38,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:574053,575387}I'll tell you this.{NOTE:一つ教えてやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.14,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:578057,580142}My parents were killed by a Rider.{NOTE:俺の親はライダーに殺された。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.10,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:583729,585106}By… a Rider?{NOTE:ライダーに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:585106,586190}Exactly.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:586190,588901}By a so-called "fellow Rider".{NOTE:お前の言うライダー同士にな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.40,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:588901,590402}But why…?{NOTE:何で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:55.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:591362,595407}You can't escape it. Even among Riders, people just think differently.{NOTE:ライダーの中にも考え方の違うやつがいるってことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.66,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:596325,597660}So that's why…{NOTE:だからって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.66,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:598994,601664}But a Rider… killing another Rider?{NOTE:ライダーが…ライダーを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.16,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:602748,604166}I can't believe it.{NOTE:信じられん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.67,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:605459,607670}There you have it.{NOTE:だからなぜなのか突き止めてえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.79,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:608796,611799}Does Avinia have anything to do with that?{NOTE:そのこととアユリアは何か関係があるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:614802,617054}What a boring, off-topic question.{NOTE:つまんねえ話をしちまったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:617054,619723}Man, you really irritate me no matter how you look at it.{NOTE:どうもお前といると調子狂うぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:619723,621723}Mr. Best-Rider-in-the-world.{NOTE:世界一のライダー君。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:622643,625187}Come on now, give me your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:さあ、絆石をよこしな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.02,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:625187,627022}I can't do that.{NOTE:それはできない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.39,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:627022,628399}But…!{NOTE:けど…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.77,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:628399,629775}But what?{NOTE:何だよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.44,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:629775,631443}If your story is true…{NOTE:お前の話がホントなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:631443,632945}…I can't forgive that Rider!{NOTE:…俺も許せねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.07,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:632945,635072}I absolutely cannot forgive such a Rider!{NOTE:そんなライダー絶対に許せねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.65,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:636490,638659}Oh really? But it's not like my story should concern you.{NOTE:まっ、お前には関係ない話だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.07,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:638659,640077}It does!{NOTE:関係ある！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:640536,642621}We're fellow Riders!{NOTE:同じライダー同士だろ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:642621,646125}If there's a Rider that raises their hand against another, I'll fight them together with you!{NOTE:ライダーを倒すライダーがいるなら俺も一緒に戦う！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.42,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:648586,650421}You're funny, you know that!{NOTE:面白えな、お前。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.67,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:650421,652673}Lute is just that kind of guy!{NOTE:リュートはそういうやつだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.09,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:652673,656093}Did you enter the Ebon Riders to defeat that guy?{NOTE:お前そいつを倒すためにブラｯクライダーズに入ったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:02.34,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:658679,662349}Do you collect Kinship Stones in order to find them?{NOTE:絆石狩りをしてるのもそのライダーを捜すためなのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:663017,665686}There is only one thing I need to do.{NOTE:俺のやるべきことはただ一つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.60,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:665686,667605}And that's to become the strongest Rider.{NOTE:最強のライダーになることだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:668314,670524}Then I'll avenge my parents!{NOTE:そして親の敵を討つ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.36,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:673485,674361}Back then…{NOTE:前に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.57,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:675196,677573}Cheval once said something similar.{NOTE:シュヴァルも同じようなことを言ってた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:24.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:678490,684454}He wanted to become the strongest Rider to defeat the Black Blight that took his mother from him.{NOTE:親を奪った黒の凶気に打ち勝つために最強のライダーになるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.70,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:685247,688709}But now he believes in kinship.{NOTE:でも今は絆の力を信じてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:688709,691212}The strength and power between a Rider and their Monstie.{NOTE:仲間やオトモンたちとの絆の力を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:692254,693589}What do you want to say?{NOTE:何が言いたい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.76,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:694423,697760}If you're trying to do everything by yourself…{NOTE:もしお前が一人で何でもやろうとしてるなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:41.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:697760,701013}…I want you to believe in the power of kinship.{NOTE:…絆の力を信じてほしいなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:48.14,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:702223,708145}B-Both of Lute's parents lost their lives while fighting the Black Blight, too.{NOTE:リュ…リュートの親父さんもママさんも黒の凶気に立ち向かって命を落とした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.27,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:708145,710272}So what do you want to say!?{NOTE:だから何が言いたいんだよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.73,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:710272,711732}You see, uh…{NOTE:だから、その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.19,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:711732,713192}How should I put this…{NOTE:何だ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:713192,715653}Both Lute and Cheval understand your feelings—{NOTE:リュートやシュヴァルならお前の気持ちをだな—}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.61,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:715653,717613}Fine, fine, thank you!{NOTE:はいはいどーもな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.36,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:717613,720366}This is why I don't like kids.{NOTE:これだからがきは面倒なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.53,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:720366,723535}Are the Ebon Riders really your true friends?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズはお前のホントの仲間なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.24,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:723535,726247}Beats me. I never really thought about it.{NOTE:さあな。考えたこともねえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.08,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:726247,728082}Then why!?{NOTE:じゃあ何で!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.29,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:728082,731293}I can become the strongest Rider with them.{NOTE:あそこにいりゃ最強のライダーになれるからだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.00,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:731293,734004}But real strength lies in the power of the kinship!{NOTE:本当の強さは絆の力だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:18.34,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:734004,738342}Then hand it over. The Kinship Stone that harbors this "real strength"!{NOTE:だったらよこせ。その本当の強さを持つ絆石をな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:738342,739635}Dusk!{NOTE:ダスク！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.31,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:755776,757319}Why?!{NOTE:何でだよ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.27,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:757319,758279}Why what?!{NOTE:何がだ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.03,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:760906,763033}We don't want to fight you!{NOTE:俺たちはお前と戦いたくない！}
Comment: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:46.03,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:766036,766036}Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.95,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:766620,767955}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:768998,770040}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Comment: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:50.04,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:770040,770040}#Black screen
Comment: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:52.04,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:772041,772041}$Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.04,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:776045,776045}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.64,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:784680,788642}Well then, if you don't want to fight me,\Nthen hand over your Kinship Stone!{NOTE:さあ！戦いたくないなら絆石をよこせ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.64,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:788642,789643}I can't do it!{NOTE:できない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:789643,792604}It holds my kinship with Ratha and everyone else!{NOTE:これにはレウスやみんなとの絆が詰まってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.89,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:792604,794898}Then I'll have to take it by force.{NOTE:だったら奪うしかないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.31,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:794898,797318}Dusk! Thunder Strike!{NOTE:ダスク！龍光まといだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.29,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:818964,820299}Dragon Breath!{NOTE:拡散龍ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.88,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:821216,821884}Ratha!{NOTE:レウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:50.35,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:827848,830351}Nowhere to run, kid!{NOTE:逃げ回ってんじゃねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:831101,832019}Stop!{NOTE:やめろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:832019,833812}I don't want to fight you!{NOTE:戦いたくない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.56,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:833812,835564}Whatever, just show it already!{NOTE:いいから出せよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:835564,838192}The new power you gained with the Rite of Channeling!{NOTE:伝承の儀で得た新たな力を！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.19,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:838192,839193}No!{NOTE:嫌だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.69,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:839193,841695}Can you still say that after this?{NOTE:これでもそう言ってられるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:842780,843989}Ratha!{NOTE:レウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.70,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:846283,849703}See? Your Monstie wants to fight!{NOTE:ほら！お前のオトモンはやる気だぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.49,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:849703,852498}Wrong! Ratha is angry!{NOTE:違う！レウスは怒ってるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:852498,853832}He says he doesn't want to fight, either.{NOTE:戦いたくないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.58,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:856001,857586}He's very angry!{NOTE:ものすごく怒ってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:858128,859922}What's with you?{NOTE:何なんだ、お前ら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.96,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:860714,861965}Are you friends or something?{NOTE:友達か！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:861965,863759}We're more than that!{NOTE:それ以上だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.92,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:863759,866929}Lute and Ratha are bound by real kinship.{NOTE:リュートとレウスは本物の絆で結ばれてるからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.80,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:868514,870808}We want to save Avinia!{NOTE:俺たちはアユリアを助けたい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.55,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:870808,872559}Then beat me.{NOTE:だったら俺を倒して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.14,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:872559,875145}If you do, I'll tell you where she is.{NOTE:お嬢ちゃんの居場所を聞き出せばいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.31,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:875145,876313}I'm not lying.{NOTE:教えてやるぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.60,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:876313,878607}But only if you fight me without running around.{NOTE:逃げ回らずに戦えばな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:879483,881318}Yeah, or are you scared of Master Gale?{NOTE:怖いんだろ？ゲイルさまが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.15,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:881318,884154}You don't stand a chance against him!{NOTE:お前らやられっぱなしだもんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:884154,885364}What are you saying?{NOTE:何を言う!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:885364,888826}If Lute and Ratha get serious, it's all over for you!{NOTE:リｭートとレウスが本気出せばお前らなんかけちょんけちょんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.32,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,890327}Fine then…!{NOTE:だったら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:890327,893831}Fight me and make me tell you where the girl is!{NOTE:俺と戦ってお嬢ちゃんの居場所を聞き出せ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:893831,896083}What do we do, Lute?{NOTE:どうする？リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.95,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:896083,896959}It's no use.{NOTE:駄目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:57.91,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:896959,897918}I can't!{NOTE:できない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:02.84,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:897918,902840}The girl will continue to be locked up unless you fight me.{NOTE:俺に勝たねえとお嬢ちゃんは捕らわれの身のままだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:07.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:902840,907511}Even if you keep her, you won't get any information on the secret art from her.{NOTE:そんなことしててもお前たちが知りたい秘術ってやつは手に入らない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:13.76,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:907511,913767}Besides, what you're doing could cause another Black Blight all over again!{NOTE:それどころかお前たちがしていることはまた黒の凶気を引き起こすかもしれないんだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:913767,914685}Huh?{NOTE:はあ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:914685,915978}What's this nonsense?{NOTE:何だそりゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:916687,918355}Cheval was just like you.{NOTE:シュヴァルもそうだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:918355,921900}Because he wanted revenge, because he wanted to become stronger and stronger…{NOTE:復讐したい強くなりたいって気持ちのせいで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.48,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:923277,925487}I'm the one who will be the next Redan!{NOTE:レダンになるのはこの俺だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.70,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:931285,935706}He was almost swallowed up by the Black Blight he hated so much.{NOTE:あんなに憎んでた黒の凶気に自分ものまれそうになってた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:39.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:935706,939251}That's the path you're heading down now!{NOTE:お前がしようとしていることはそういうことだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.54,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:939251,942546}So, no matter what, I won't fight you!{NOTE:だから！絶対お前とは戦いたくない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.75,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:942546,944756}And I'm sure Avinia thinks the same!{NOTE:アユリアもきっと同じことを思ってる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:947551,950554}I've never heard anything about a secret art from Avinia.{NOTE:アユリアから秘術の話なんか聞いたことない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:950554,952181}I'll bet she doesn't even know about it.{NOTE:きっと知らないはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.76,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:952181,954766}So please give her back!{NOTE:だから、アユリアをかえしてくれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:09.99,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:969281,969990}Hmm?{NOTE:おや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.78,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:969990,971783}Is that Gale's humming, I hear?{NOTE:ゲイルの鼻歌だね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:12.86,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:971783,972868}Did you like it?{NOTE:気に入ったのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.87,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:974286,976872}Somehow I feel like I've heard it before.{NOTE:何だか知っているような気がするんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:18.95,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:978040,978957}This song, I mean.{NOTE:この歌を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:26.84,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:986173,986840}So?{NOTE:何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.75,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:986840,987758}What now?{NOTE:どうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:987758,989468}What are you thinking?{NOTE:何考えてる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.13,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:989468,992137}Did you finally change your mind about Avinia?{NOTE:かえしてくれる気になったのか？アユリアを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.76,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:994264,995766}Fine.{NOTE:いいだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:995766,998977}I'll tell you where she's being held.{NOTE:教えてやるよ、あのお嬢ちゃんの居場所をな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:998977,1000187}Really?!{NOTE:ホントか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000187,1001021}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.14,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001313,1004149}Really, really, really, really, really, for real!?{NOTE:ホントにホントにホントにホントにホントなんだろうな!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.69,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005067,1006693}Shut up, Whiskers!{NOTE:しつこいぞヒゲ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:47.90,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006693,1007903}Wh…{NOTE:ヒ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007903,1008862}Don't call me "Whiskers"!{NOTE:ヒゲ言うな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011490,1012407}Come with me.{NOTE:ついてこい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015244,1016411}Let's go, Ratha.{NOTE:行こうレウス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.14,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037224,1039142}No one is watching here.{NOTE:ここなら誰も見てねえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:22.14,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040394,1042145}Oh! We finally know what his face looks like!{NOTE:初めて素顔を見せたな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.90,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043522,1046900}What? Is Master Gale too cool for you to comprehend?{NOTE:さてはゲイルさまがカッコ良過ぎて驚いてるな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:30.86,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049945,1050862}Come on.{NOTE:ほい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:35.24,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051697,1055242}Let's shake on our truce.{NOTE:さあ、仲直りの握手といこうじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055242,1057869}Do you think we can trust him, Lute?{NOTE:リュート信じて大丈夫なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.25,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062541,1064251}Master Gale doesn't go back on his words.{NOTE:ゲイルさまに二言はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065294,1066628}Hey, Gale.{NOTE:なあ、ゲイル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.46,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066628,1070465}What are you going to do after you return Avinia?{NOTE:アユリアをかえしてくれた後お前はどうなるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.38,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070465,1073385}Hey, come on. Now you're worried about me?{NOTE:おいおい、今度は俺の心配か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.84,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074219,1076847}Will you keep hanging out with the other Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズに居続けるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076847,1078307}I told you already.{NOTE:言ったはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.39,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078307,1080392}I will become the strongest Rider.{NOTE:俺は最強のライダーになると。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.89,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081143,1082894}I'm going my own way.{NOTE:俺は俺の道を行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:09.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085230,1089401}Besides, you don't want to fight me either, do you?{NOTE:お前だって俺ともう戦いたくないだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.61,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097618,1098619}Lute!?{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102080,1104041}Your Kinship Stone is gone!{NOTE:ニャい！絆石！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.50,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105667,1107502}I can't believe you fools!{NOTE:バカなやつらだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107502,1108629}You…!{NOTE:お前…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.17,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108629,1110172}Don't be too angry.{NOTE:怒るなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:33.17,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110172,1113175}Now that I have this we can't fight anymore.\NJust like you wanted, right?{NOTE:これでホントにお前とはもう戦えなくなっただろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.22,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1115761,1117220}– Give it back!\N– Whoa.{NOTE:—返せ！この！\\N—おっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118221,1120015}Are you alright, Navirou?{NOTE:大丈夫か!?ナビルー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120015,1121475}I-I'm fine!{NOTE:だ、大丈夫だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.72,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121475,1122726}But Lute…!{NOTE:てか、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.47,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122726,1124478}That's my Kinship Stone!{NOTE:それは俺の絆石だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.43,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125228,1126438}Not anymore.{NOTE:もう俺のだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.14,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126438,1128148}No, it's still mine!{NOTE:いいや俺のだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128148,1129983}There's no way you'll be able to use it!{NOTE:お前に使えるはずがない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.77,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129983,1131777}We'll see about that…{NOTE:そいつはどうかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:52.94,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132194,1132944}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133654,1134529}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136490,1140077}Look like you're right. No reaction at all.{NOTE:何てな。そりゃ反応しないよな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:03.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140077,1143914}So each Kinship Stone only works for the Rider it's given to?{NOTE:絆石はライダー一人に一つずつ授けられるものだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.79,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143914,1144790}That's right.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.96,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144790,1148960}That Kinship Stone holds my bond with Ratha and my friends.{NOTE:その絆石にはレウスや仲間との絆が詰まってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.54,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148960,1151546}But, for you, it's just a piece of jewelry.{NOTE:お前がつけてもただの石だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151546,1153590}That's how the power of kinship works.{NOTE:絆の力ってそういうもんだろ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154925,1156134}I guess you're right.{NOTE:そうだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156134,1159513}So why are you hunting for the Kinship Stones?{NOTE:なのに何で絆石狩りなんてしてるんだよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.93,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159513,1161932}It's not like you can even use them!{NOTE:奪ったって使いようがないのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161932,1164893}What if they want to erase Riders from this world?{NOTE:ひょっとしてこの世からライダーを消すためか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.27,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166770,1169272}Everything is a part of Master Anvis's plan.{NOTE:全てはアンヴィスさまのお考えだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.10,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169272,1171108}And what exactly is his plan?{NOTE:何なんだよその考えって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:35.52,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172067,1175529}Does the secret of Avinia's village have something to do with it?{NOTE:アユリアの村の秘術ってやつと関係あるんだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.44,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175529,1176446}Beats me.{NOTE:さあな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.11,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177906,1179116}Catch.{NOTE:ほらよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.11,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179741,1181118}Master Gale?!{NOTE:ゲイルさま!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.57,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181118,1183578}We can't use it anyway, so what's the harm?{NOTE:使えない絆石に用はないだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:48.20,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183578,1188208}But Master Anvis told us to get his Kinship Stone because of its vast power…{NOTE:でもアンヴィスさまはこいつの絆石は力があるから取ってこいって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188208,1189626}It's not that vast.{NOTE:大したことはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189626,1191044}Yes it is! Super vast!{NOTE:大したことあるぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191044,1192212}Navirou, don't!{NOTE:ナビルーよせ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193046,1194047}It's okay.{NOTE:いいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.71,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194047,1195716}That thing has no value to me…{NOTE:別にこいつのでなくたって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197217,1198593}…without that guy.{NOTE:どうせ意味がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199052,1200137}Come on, let's go.{NOTE:さあ、行くぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.76,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200137,1201763}B-But…{NOTE:いや、でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.88,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201763,1202889}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202889,1204307}Wait, Gale!{NOTE:待て、ゲイル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.81,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205350,1206810}What is it this time?{NOTE:まだ何か用か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.31,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207644,1209312}You still haven't told me where Avinia is.{NOTE:アユリアの居場所を聞いてない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.64,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209896,1211648}And you promised you would.{NOTE:教えるって約束だったろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.69,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212899,1214693}There's no point in telling you now.{NOTE:教えたところで意味がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215610,1218196}You lack the power to rescue that girl.{NOTE:お前にあのお嬢ちゃんは助け出せない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.32,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218196,1219322}I'll show you that I can save her!{NOTE:助けてみせる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:25.57,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220240,1225579}The moment you guys step into the Black Castle, you're done for.{NOTE:お前らじゃブラックキャッスルに足を踏み入れた途端たたきのめされて終わりだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.83,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225579,1227831}Black Castle, huh?{NOTE:ブラｯクキｬｯスルというのだな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.91,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227831,1229916}So that's where your hideout is?{NOTE:お前たちのアジトは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.75,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229916,1232753}Whether you think we're done for or not…{NOTE:たたきのめされようが何があろうが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.96,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232753,1234963}…we'll go rescue her anyway!{NOTE:…俺たちはアユリアを助けに行く！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.84,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236840,1238842}You might not be able to escape with your lives.{NOTE:生きて帰れないかもしれないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239634,1241219}Doesn't matter, I'll still go.{NOTE:それでも行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244264,1245599}Ah… Hey!{NOTE:あっ…おい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.64,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245599,1246641}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246641,1247684}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.56,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249102,1251563}A place where the sun can be seen setting in the eastern sea.{NOTE:東の海に日が沈む場所。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.35,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251563,1253356}Master Gale?!{NOTE:ゲイルさま!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.06,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253356,1255066}You'll find the Black Castle there.{NOTE:ブラックキャッスルはそこにある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.69,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257527,1258693}Come and get some if you want!{NOTE:来るなら来い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.90,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258693,1260906}It'll be your graveyard!{NOTE:そこがお前らの死に場所となる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.99,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267871,1269998}What a noisy fella.{NOTE:何て一言多いやつだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269998,1271833}Even more than you, Navirou?{NOTE:ナビルー以上だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271833,1273043}Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.71,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273043,1274711}But we did it, Lute!{NOTE:でもやったなリュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274711,1276463}Now we know where they're holding Avinia!{NOTE:アユリアの居場所が分かったぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277380,1278215}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:24.26,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281551,1284262}A place where the sun can be seen setting in the eastern sea?{NOTE:東の海に日が沈む場所？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.59,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284262,1287599}That's what that Gale guy said?{NOTE:そう言ってたのね？ゲイルってやつが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287599,1289851}Yeah. That's the way I remember him putting it.{NOTE:ああ。確かにそう言ってた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.39,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289851,1291394}But can we believe him…?{NOTE:ホントかなぁ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:36.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291394,1296733}He was vague but I don't think he was lying.{NOTE:あいつつかみどころがないやつだけど嘘を言ってるようには思えなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.11,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297567,1300111}I don't think I can trust Gale's words.{NOTE:ゲイルのことは信用できない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300111,1302906}But if Lute goes, I'll go too.{NOTE:でもリュートが行くっていうなら俺も行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.86,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302906,1303865}Me too.{NOTE:私も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.90,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303865,1304908}Me too.{NOTE:僕も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.86,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304908,1306868}Of course, I'll go too!{NOTE:もちろん自分もっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:50.24,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306868,1310247}Nariki, you're still a new Rider, you'll only make them worry.{NOTE:ナリキはまだ新米ライダーだし心配だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.79,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310247,1311790}That's not true!{NOTE:そんなことないっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.37,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311790,1314376}I can be useful too.{NOTE:自分も役に立ってみせるっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:58.50,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314376,1318505}I can't keep still now that we know where Avinia is.{NOTE:アユリアの居場所が分かったっていうのにじっとしてられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.42,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318505,1320423}That's right. We'll go with you!{NOTE:そうだよ。僕らも行くよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322342,1323510}All right.{NOTE:分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:09.68,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323510,1329683}By the way, isn't the place where the sun sets into the eastern sea… around here on this map?{NOTE:ちなみに東の海に日が沈む場所というと地図上ではこの辺りでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.18,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330392,1334187}Looks like Itsy-Bits was actually right.{NOTE:イチビッツの言ってたこと間違いじゃなかったようだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.18,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334187,1336189}But his map is still too hard to read.{NOTE:ざっくりし過ぎだけれどね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.77,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339234,1341778}Lute? What are you thinking about?{NOTE:リュート？何か気になってる？}
